file_content.text: Not the way I would have picked.
It's Vaylin! She'll bring the whole city crashing down on you if she has to!
I'm starting to doubt more than your screening process.
Difficult for me to blame you right now....
I don't think I like your pilot's sense of humor.
Be sure to let him know--if you get to meet him.
We have them for sure! They couldn't possibly escape through there.
Now, now... let's not take any chances.
Lana? are my scanners glitched? Did you just charge headfirst into a Skytrooper droid factory?
Vaylin's almost on us! We're out of options!
This is Altair Three all over again....
We can handle a few droids! Come on!
